desc.en: The Rongchen Rail Transit is a means of transportation under the Rongchen Transportation Operation Co., Ltd. (a private enterprise). No matter how far the distance is, the ticket price is always only 4 yuan. The Rongchen Rail Transit is the first rail transit system in Rongchen City and is loved by the vast number of people in Rongchen City.
desc.zh-Hans: 容晨轨道交通是容晨交通运营有限公司（私人企业）旗下的交通工具，也是容晨市首个轨道交通系统，深受当地群众喜爱。无论行程多远，票价始终为4元。
